{"tid":2285744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"善心小店送暖：辛苦得嚟開心  政府無情 民間自救 失業壯年等派飯","createTime":"2020-11-14T11:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T12:59:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6991114bb9a1f273e8a5114b8c1ea369ee5b9be","tid":2285744,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/LF7V2OHPPRB73M7NQTHDSBRD3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FLF7V2OHPPRB73M7NQTHDSBRD3Q%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=2d01ced9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FLF7V2OHPPRB73M7NQTHDSBRD3Q%2F&h=d17f87ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/LF7V2OHPPRB73M7NQTHDSBRD3Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n善心小店送暖：辛苦得嚟開心 <br />\n政府無情 民間自救 失業壯年等派飯<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府抗疫不力，本港經濟受疫情重挫，百業蕭條，打工仔需減薪甚至被裁員，失業人數接近26萬，創16年來新高。普羅基層在政府「商家為先」抗疫政策下未能受惠，更面臨三餐不繼。然而政府無情，民間自救，旺角太子區多間食店及車行向基層派飯送暖，有人出身草根希望回饋社會、有人每月派出6,000個飯盒，有人發現多了中年人及年輕人輪候。他們指現時社會氣氛沉重，能做的是繼續為基層送上窩心暖意，盼一起渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：忍受途人目光「為生存冇得揀」<br />\n<br />\n位於太子基隆街的「愛心飯團」，創辦人黃國權本身經營車行，派飯是他的「副業」。今年開始，疫情來勢洶洶，眼見社會經濟受到嚴重打擊，。。。。。。。。。。。。。一定要講多謝同身體健康，唔可以用有色眼光對佢哋，畀佢哋覺得係尊重，而唔係施捨」。他說希望對方明白逆境只是一時的事，終能捱過困境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6QFr_OwmH09KftRHcDHAH1YDKWE=/4737x2657/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ICCOT3JM3JHB5P7YKV776QKOO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6QFr_OwmH09KftRHcDHAH1YDKWE%3D%2F4737x2657%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FICCOT3JM3JHB5P7YKV776QKOO4.jpg&h=16d3d698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■太子食店「阿媽靚湯」獲熱心人士贊助派發素食飯盒送暖，每日下午都有大批市民排隊輪候。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八號風球照排隊<br />\n<br />\n每天早上，車水馬龍的太子彌敦道總有一條人龍，各人拿着籌號於齋舖「百寶齋廚」外守候，只。。。。。。。。。。。。。。餐廳開業六年，負責人高女士於疫情下每天早午合共派發800個飯盒。<br />\n<br />\n疫情下各行業步入寒冬，不少壯年人士淪為失業大軍，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，淪為失業大軍輪候免費飯。<br />\n<br />\n太子區內有不少補習社，惟疫情下長時間停課，補。。。。。。。。。。。，三小時後每個輪候者都拿着飯盒安心離開。<br />\n<br />\n高女士雖然每天派飯，。。。。。。。。。。。。，不諱言明年5月租約期滿後若業主加租，極可能要結業。<br />\n<br />\n區內另一善心食肆「徐記廚房」，。。。。。。。。。。。。，已遞上飯盒給店外輪候人士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IQtTgQfa3orpt8FHR7otODQnEe8=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6XSRHAZICNC2DDYZ5GYVOZTBHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIQtTgQfa3orpt8FHR7otODQnEe8%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6XSRHAZICNC2DDYZ5GYVOZTBHU.jpg&h=5a89a0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「愛心飯團」黃國權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8IlKH_MngI_jaGcDRNLNE0QLnbw=/1580x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KNU7VIDXSZHOTOBJZK3OCNAKYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8IlKH_MngI_jaGcDRNLNE0QLnbw%3D%2F1580x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKNU7VIDXSZHOTOBJZK3OCNAKYI.jpg&h=cfc1cf99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「百寶齋廚」高女士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清潔工拉隊「懲罰」<br />\n<br />\n過去一年多的社會運動與疫情，徐媽媽將不定期派飯改為每周舉行，更與義工組織「初見」、土炮湯水店「到家元朗」合作派飯幫助基層。當日所見，義工向街上清潔工遞上飯盒，弓着腰在垃圾房工作的清潔姨姨隨即展開笑顏，稱「返屋企有得食」。徐媽媽憶述一次清潔工拉隊「懲罰」徐記廚房，叮囑她一定要照單收錢，令她深深感動。<br />\n<br />\n同區另一間食店「阿媽靚湯」6月獲熱心人士贊助派發素食飯盒送暖，。。。。。。。。。。。，廚師要由午市高峯時段直落到落場時段，但「辛苦得嚟開心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ULtogtkT95Kkv39-YNiT_VTx9yE=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M77JODMTJBAOXIB3ZZHIQ6L7JU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FULtogtkT95Kkv39-YNiT_VTx9yE%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM77JODMTJBAOXIB3ZZHIQ6L7JU.jpg&h=144841f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「徐記廚房」徐媽媽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kQnv8ToXX2zYUXIiurd-VTAWfW0=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HCJC56ESVFA3RBERXIBA6FA5FM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkQnv8ToXX2zYUXIiurd-VTAWfW0%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHCJC56ESVFA3RBERXIBA6FA5FM.jpg&h=eb964e90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「阿媽靚湯」劉先生"},{"pid":"37bbc7a9c4d3276e3b2d19d04abdaaecb1003ec1","tid":2285744,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"人間有情 !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}